(38, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, '安卓  车族宝：我要加盟、提现、银行卡BUG；合富通：我的推荐人，强制更新 BUG 2016.07.20', '', 3, 2, 'codeerror', 'android', '', '', '', '<p><br /></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;">2016.07.20</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"><span>安卓</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;">-<span>车族宝</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;">1</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;">.<span>我要加盟，保持与</span><span>ios</span><span>一致。如图，其中联系人和手机号从后台读取；</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><img src="data/upload/1/201607/2010295703847t04.png" alt="" /><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"><span>2.</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"><span>提现，在提交按钮睇下，加一行提示，</span>“注意：只支持体现到本人银行卡”</span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><img src="data/upload/1/201607/20103011068n9t.png" alt="" /></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"><span>3.</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"><span>银行卡，现在已添加的银行卡，不能进行删除，添加一个删除的功能；</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><img src="data/upload/1/201607/2010302406985in9.png" alt="" /><span style="font-family:Calibri;font-size:10.5pt;">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;">4.<span>新增银行卡，里面身份证号码和开户名先从后台预读取，后台没有的，就手工输入；</span></span><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;"></span></p>\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:''宋体'';font-size:10.5pt;">&nbs